    "description": {
      "zh": "由ELCAN公司设计制造的SpecterDR（双用途）1x/4x瞄准镜，是Specter瞄准镜系列的第一款真正具有“双模式”的瞄具，它象征着光学瞄具领域的新突破， 仅需旋钮操作即可实现4x至1x倍率的缩放切换。 ",
      "en": "The SpecterDR (Dual Role) 1x/4x scope from Specter scope series designed by ELCAN has marked a breakthrough in the optic sight development by becoming the first variable scope that truly has two work modes, switching from 4x magnification to 1x in one touch. Also features a backup iron sight."
